    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy for pump-induced hemolysis (mean NIH error 8.3%, RH < 1 for all worst-case variants). The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given the medium model influence and established simulation practices. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
